App usage/license metering	‚ùå	‚úîÔ∏è
Browser/web analytics	‚ùå	‚úîÔ∏è

Bottom line:

    Citrix DaaS Monitor is for broad health and alerting.
    uberAgent is for deep, actionable troubleshooting and optimization.

